by paradajozsef at 2016-01-18T21:44:23Z

:+1:

One more thing to note. If such a yml is provided to the loader:

```yml
Acme\MyObj:
    attributes:
        foo:
            groups: 'group1'
```

```Invalid argument supplied for foreach()``` warning raises, because it is [not ensured here](https://github.com/symfony/symfony/blob/2.7/src/Symfony/Component/Serializer/Mapping/Loader/YamlFileLoader.php#L76).

If you think this should be in another PR, than sorry. :)

